Sazka Investors Will Vote on Chief’s Removal, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-03-15T07:09:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/sazka-investors-will-vote-on-chief-s-removal-hospodarske-says.html
Sazka AS stockholders will vote at
an extraordinary meeting today on proposal to remove Chief
Executive Officer Ales Husak from his job at the lottery
company,  Hospodarske Noviny  reported, citing the company.  The shareholders will also vote on proposals to change
Sazka’s articles of incorporation which would allow investors
such as Penta Investments Ltd. to enter the company, the
newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  